{"word":"H5358 - נָקַם - nâqam - naw-kam' - Avenge","slug":"H5358","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָקַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nâqam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-kam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Avenge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05E7;&#x05DD; - na&#x0302;qam</b> - <i>naw-kam'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>grudge</i>, that is, <i>avenge</i> or <i>punish: - </i>avenge (-r, self), punish, revenge (self), X surely, take vengeance."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5359\">H5359</a>, <a href=\"#/H5360\">H5360</a>"}]}